name: fastq
query: SELECT cancer_path as fastq, human_sex as sex FROM human as h JOIN cancer as c ON h.human_id = c.human_id;

name: manfastq
query: SELECT cancer_path as man_fastq FROM human as h JOIN cancer as c ON h.human_id = c.human_id WHERE h.human_sex = 'man';

name: ?fastq
query: SELECT ? FROM human as h JOIN cancer as c ON h.human_id = c.human_id WHERE h.human_sex = '?';
